    <title>解决小程序 app.js中的onLaunch中的数据 在page的onLoade中接收不到的问题</title>
    <url>/2020/03/09/xiaochegnxu/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="一、问题阐述"><a href="#一、问题阐述" class="headerlink" title="一、问题阐述"></a>一、问题阐述</h3><p>​      由于工作的安排，最近在改我们公司的一个小程序，在此期间碰到了一个坑，遇到的问题是，实现登录时，app.js中 onLaunch 实现数据请求拿到后端返回的参数后写入 Storage ，然后在首页 Storage 取信息，但是并未能取到这个参数。调试后发现  app.js onLaunch并没有先于onLoad 执行完再执行，而是onLoad先执行完 ，所以进入首页未能取到相关参数。<a id="more"></a>跟踪了一下问题发现，app.js onLaunch  中登录的请求时异步的，这就可能导致请求的参数在page onLoade 执行完后才会返回。</p>
<h3 id="二、解决办法"><a href="#二、解决办法" class="headerlink" title="二、解决办法"></a>二、解决办法</h3><h3 id="1-第一种方法：定义一个回调函数-。"><a href="#1-第一种方法：定义一个回调函数-。" class="headerlink" title="1 . 第一种方法：定义一个回调函数 。"></a>1 . 第一种方法：定义一个回调函数 。</h3><p>​       Page页面判断一下当前app.globalData.employId是否有值，如果没有（第一次）则定义定义一个app方法（回调函数）app.employIdCallback = employId =&gt; {…}。App页面在请求success后判断时候有Page页面定义的回调方法，如果有就执行该方法 ，实现代码：</p>
<p>​        app.js </p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">reLogin: <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params">app</span>) </span>&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">       <span class="comment">// 执行登录，获取用户身份标识openid</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">       <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"2.现在执行到 reLogin"</span>);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">var</span> that = <span class="keyword">this</span>;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//return new Promise((resolve, reject) =&gt; &#123;</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">       swan.login(&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           success: <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params">res</span>) </span>&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">               <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(res);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">               <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"3.现在执行到  swan.login"</span>);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">               swan.request(&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                   url: that.globalData.loginUrl,</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                   data: &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       act: <span class="string">'BDXCXlogin'</span>,</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       code: res.code,</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                   &#125;,</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                   success: <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params">res</span>) </span>&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       <span class="comment">// swan.setStorageSync("sessionid", res.header["Set-Cookie"]);</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"login check statusCode:"</span> + res.statusCode);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"4.现在请求后台登录"</span>);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(res.data);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       <span class="keyword">if</span> (res.statusCode == <span class="number">200</span>) &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                           <span class="keyword">var</span> result = <span class="built_in">JSON</span>.parse(res.data);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                          <span class="comment">// var result = res.data;</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                           <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"result的val："</span> + result);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                           <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"result.retcode的值："</span> + result.retcode);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                           <span class="keyword">if</span> (result.retcode == <span class="string">'SUCCESS'</span>) &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                               swan.setStorage(&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                                   key: <span class="string">""</span> + that.globalData.tokenName + <span class="string">""</span>,</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                                   data: <span class="string">""</span> + result.token + <span class="string">""</span>,</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                                   success: <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params"></span>) </span>&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                                       <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"登录成功后将token存储完成：storage token success"</span>);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                                   &#125;,</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                                   fail: <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params"></span>) </span>&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                                       <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"storage token failed"</span>);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                                   &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                               &#125;)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                               <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"当前token"</span> + result.token);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                               <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"现在执行 resolve1"</span>);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                               <span class="comment">//resolve(result.token);</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                               <span class="keyword">if</span> (that.employIdCallback) &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                                   that.employIdCallback(result.token);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                               &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                           &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                               <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"login check failed:"</span> + result.retmsg);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                               <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"现在执行 reject1"</span>);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                               <span class="comment">// reject(result.retmsg);</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                           &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                           <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"login request network error:"</span> + res.statusCode);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                           swan.showToast(&#123; <span class="attr">icon</span>: <span class="string">'none'</span>, <span class="attr">title</span>: <span class="string">'login request network error:'</span> + res.statusCode + <span class="string">''</span> &#125;)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                           <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"现在执行 reject2"</span>);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                           <span class="comment">//  reject(res.statusCode);</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       <span class="comment">//resolve(result.token);</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                   &#125;,</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                   fail: <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params">res</span>) </span>&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"现在执行 reject3"</span>);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       <span class="comment">// reject(res);</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(res);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"login request failed"</span>);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       swan.showToast(&#123; <span class="attr">icon</span>: <span class="string">'none'</span>, <span class="attr">title</span>: <span class="string">'login request failed'</span> &#125;)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                   &#125;,</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                   complete: <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params">res</span>) </span>&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">'login request completed'</span>);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       swan.hideLoading();</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                       swan.hideNavigationBarLoading();</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                   &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">               &#125;);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           &#125;,</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           fail: <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params">err</span>) </span>&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">               <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">'swan login fail'</span>, err);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">       &#125;);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">       <span class="comment">// &#125;)</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   &#125;</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>​          indx.js</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">onLoad(query) &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">       <span class="comment">// 页面加载 </span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">var</span> that = <span class="keyword">this</span>;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">       <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"现在进入webview.js"</span>);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">       <span class="built_in">console</span>.info(<span class="string">`Page onLoad with query: <span class="subst">$&#123;<span class="built_in">JSON</span>.stringify(query)&#125;</span>`</span>);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">       <span class="built_in">console</span>.info(query);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">var</span> token = swan.getStorageSync(app.globalData.tokenName);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">if</span> (token.length &gt; <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"webview.js  getStorageSync 获取  token&gt;&gt;"</span> + token);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           <span class="keyword">this</span>.setData(&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">               weburl: <span class="string">''</span> + app.globalData.weburl + <span class="string">'?tokenData='</span> + token + <span class="string">''</span>,</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           &#125;)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">       &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           <span class="comment">// app.reLogin().then((res) =&gt; &#123;</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           <span class="comment">//     var token = swan.getStorageSync(app.globalData.tokenName);</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           <span class="comment">//     console.log('现在执行app.reLogin().then' +token);</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           <span class="comment">//     console.log('当前res数据:' + res);</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           <span class="comment">//     console.log('token2' + res);</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           <span class="comment">//     this.setData(&#123;</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           <span class="comment">//         weburl: '' + app.globalData.weburl + '?tokenData=' + res + '',</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           <span class="comment">//     &#125;)</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           <span class="comment">// &#125;, (error) =&gt; &#123;</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           <span class="comment">//     console.log('失败：' + error)</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           <span class="comment">// &#125;)</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           <span class="comment">//为了解决小程序数据请求异步问题 ，app.js onLaunch 中数据请求的数据可能在paages  onLoad 之后才返回 </span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           app.employIdCallback = <span class="function"><span class="params">account</span> =&gt;</span> &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">               <span class="keyword">var</span> token = swan.getStorageSync(app.globalData.tokenName);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">               <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">'现在执行app.reLogin().then'</span> + token);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">               <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">'当前res数据:'</span> + account);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">               <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">'token2'</span> + token);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">               <span class="keyword">this</span>.setData(&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                   weburl: <span class="string">''</span> + app.globalData.weburl + <span class="string">'?tokenData='</span> + token + <span class="string">''</span>,</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">               &#125;)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">           &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">       &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   &#125;,</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="2-第二种方法-：-使用promise，判断进程状态，在index中去判断进程状态，再去执行页面的加载"><a href="#2-第二种方法-：-使用promise，判断进程状态，在index中去判断进程状态，再去执行页面的加载" class="headerlink" title="2. 第二种方法  ：  使用promise，判断进程状态，在index中去判断进程状态，再去执行页面的加载"></a>2. 第二种方法  ：  使用promise，判断进程状态，在index中去判断进程状态，再去执行页面的加载</h3><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> promise = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Promise</span>(<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params">resolve, reject</span>) </span>&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="comment">/* 异步操作成功 */</span>)&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> resolve(value);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> reject(error);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#125;);</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">promise.then(<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params">value</span>) </span>&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> <span class="comment">// success</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#125;, <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params">value</span>) </span>&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> <span class="comment">// failure</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#125;);</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>​     Promise 构造函数接受一个函数作为参数，该函数的两个参数分别是 resolve 方法和 reject 方法。</p>
<p>​    如果异步操作成功，则用 resolve 方法将 Promise 对象的状态，从「未完成」变为「成功」（即从 pending 变为 resolved）；</p>
<p>​    如果异步操作失败，则用 reject 方法将 Promise 对象的状态，从「未完成」变为「失败」（即从 pending 变为 rejected）。</p>
<p><strong>具体实现的代码见第一种方法中的注释部分</strong></p>
]]></content>
